e":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-01-28T10:36:07.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>佢同我舊公司經理男朋友係fd 成日帶佢女友定老婆?去食飯<br />\n明明都冇人識佢地 但次次都又要後門入 又要用布簾擋住 又指定人送菜 搞場大龍鳳<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n連我經理都話 如果唔係比面男朋友 真係唔想做佢生意 <br />\n食得少 坐得耐 要求多<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n見過咁多明星 紅過佢幾百倍既 要求都冇佢咁多<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n所以都明白點解佢紅唔起<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/bye.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n講真而家啲00後或90後期嘅後生仔都應該唔識佢啦，仲要扮大牌<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-01-28T15:51:35.000Z","msg":"講真 我92 第一次見到佢個陣都剩係覺得係電視見過 up唔出咩名 三四線茄喱啡<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"b83c7409c33c342b99e210f73eeebdc6417994be","tid":543242,"uid":121695,"like":4,"dislike":1,"score":3,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-01-28T15:54:03.000Z","msg":"鄧健泓都上神枱<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"a627a5e7766c765019af12b98a32e774e1f5bdfa","tid":543242,"uid":48083,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"quote":{"pid":"0f50c4f997f91e791211ca0b0828192073e2f906","tid":543242,"uid":56716,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-01-28T10:42:07.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote><blockquote><blockquote><blockquote><blockquote><blockquote>如果有神佢真係唱得好難聽，似俾人鍊住春袋咁。<br />\n<br />\n朋友二號，許志安一開口唱完勝。</blockquote><br />\n我唔覺佢唱歌難聽，同埋下下都同人比係無意思。</blockquote>咪係,  如果有神根本係好難唱   , 佢唱功已經算唔錯</blockquote><br />\n直上「你說去到哪裡　就與我佔領哪裡<br />\n直到世界教你佔據　就算你想要撒退<br />\n沒有世界也有我　永遠愛你　於高速公路裡」<br />\n呢段都難唱啦，佢唱得算係咁了。</blockquote>依首 喺我唔知中一中二嗰陣聽 ,  好鍾意, loop 左好多次, 啲歌詞入哂腦<br />\n同十幾廿年後我仲識唔睇歌詞唱到 <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n我都係，到而家仲可以一口氣背哂呢段出嚟<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote>難唱我唔否認，但佢高音果度我覺得好難頂，唱得好勉強。</blockquote><br />\n每人嘅睇法唔同<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/wink.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n我覺得佢唔係好好但又唔係好差嘅，啲歌又幾好聽<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hoho.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-01-28T15:59:34.000Z","msg":"同日文原唱一比差好遠<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"39f49bb512d92962605078632afd0c47336063b5","tid":543242,"uid":85030,"like":1,"dislike":1,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-01-28T16:14:51.000Z","msg":"好討厭呢個偽人<br />\n冇得解釋<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"505922e211e9ab4434ff3f1c4e635ba372f14816","tid":543242,"uid":69568,"like":0,"dislike":2,"score":-2,"quote":{"pid":"45743fb7daba39ed689dc9e1368aa4b6fa4df291","tid":543242,"uid":56716,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-01-28T10:34:08.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>心寒 世界級</blockquote><br />\n獨唱同合唱都好聽<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/good.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-01-28T17:15:12.000Z","msg":"仲要比林奕匡智會條撚樣抄埋<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"c530b04c00aa55bd8472167fdff856271efe7b98","tid":543242,"uid":82917,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-01-28T20:43:12.000Z","msg":"下佢結左婚？？"},{"pid":"7b009c9cf6b5ae93a5ef8dc0b8e4b2aef72e0014","tid":543242,"uid":99642,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"c530b04c00aa55bd8472167fdff856271efe7b98","tid":543242,"uid":82917,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-01-28T20: